3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a possibility as the paper deals with networks of nodes communicating with each other. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possibility as the paper deals with multicast capacity regions of wireless networks. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper may involve algorithms for interference alignment and communication in dense wireless networks.
